    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so like, if someone is looking to project that \"global professional\" image, what are the actual standards? like for clothing or even how you communicate in a meeting? what's the baseline for being seen as a high-level, sophisticated person internationally?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
