      "content": "For a baseline, aim for classic, conservative attire—think well-tailored suits for men and elegant, understated dresses or suits for women. In meetings, always maintain a respectful, measured tone, avoiding overly casual slang or aggressive interruptions. The real key to looking high-level is projecting an air of quiet confidence, which often means not needing to shout to be heard.",
